My question now is, what can be done to rectify this fraud and restore the integrity of our elections. If we don't, how can we ever have another trustworthy election in our country?

I hope and pray that there is a path forward, between Sidney, President Trump, the State Legislatures, and/or the courts to resolve this injustice.

Concerned, Conservative, Citizen.
 
RLO
